{"ProductId":"13","Title":"Classic™ Steel","ShortDescription":"Strength and durability in a wide range of looks and colors, so you never have to sacrifice style","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/classicsteel-ironoreshowcase.webp?sfvrsn=25b7a514_1","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/classic","Overview":"<h3>Classic Style, Features that Matter</h3><h4>Built Your Way</h4><p>Choose from 1, 2, or 3-layer steel construction so you get the right mix of durability, insulation, and budget.</p><h4>Strong Steel, Real Options</h4><p>Every door uses tough, reliable steel. Plus you can pick from short or long panel designs, add windows, or go with a wood-look <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/ultra-grain\">Ultra-Grain&reg; finish</a> for extra charm.</p><h4>Colors for Every Home</h4><p>Select from 14 popular factory colors or customize with over 1,500 <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg; paint options</a>.</p><h4>Comfort All Year</h4><p>Insulation options include <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane</a> or polystyrene which keep your garage quieter and more comfortable, with R-values up to 18.4.</p><h4>Ready for Rough Weather</h4><p><a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; door reinforcement</a> is available for homes in high-wind areas.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>How It&rsquo;s Made: Classic&trade; Steel</h3><p>The Classic&trade; Steel garage door is designed to handle daily use while looking great for years to come. You can choose from single-, double-, or triple-layer construction, with every option starting with high-quality steel for reliable strength. For insulation, pick either Intellicore&reg; polyurethane&mdash;Clopay&rsquo;s advanced foam that expands to fill the door for maximum energy efficiency and durability&mdash;or opt for solid polystyrene panels that add comfort and quiet.</p><p>The exterior steel panels are protected by a multi-layer coating system, including hot-dipped galvanizing, a special metal oxide pretreatment, and a baked-on primer and topcoat, all working together to keep rust away and the finish looking sharp. Maintenance is easy, with a replaceable vinyl bottom seal in a rust-resistant aluminum retainer blocking out water and drafts, and removable window grilles for simple cleaning.</p><p>Safety comes built in, too, thanks to the patented Safe-T-Bracket&reg; that helps prevent injury during maintenance. Insulated models also include smooth, quiet nylon rollers and heavy-duty steel hinges, so your door works smoothly every day.</p><p><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-classic-steel-full.webp?sfvrsn=1fb75eda_3\" alt=\"Classic Steel\" sf-size=\"100\" /></p><ol><li>Steel</li><li>Intellicore&reg; Polyurethane or Polystyrene Insulation</li><li>Steel</li></ol><p><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-classic-steel-valueplus-value.webp?sfvrsn=89dc6d9c_2\" alt=\"Classic Steel\" sf-size=\"100\" /></p><ol><li>Steel</li><li>Polystyrene Insulation</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Classic Steel","DisplayIndex":19,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/classic-steel","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>The Classic&trade; Steel garage door is available in a wide range of colors and finishes. Choose from classic shades like Standard White, Almond, Sandtone, Chocolate, and Desert Tan for a timeless, versatile look. For a bolder statement, select from premium colors such as Black, Bronze, Mocha Brown, Hunter Green, Gray, Charcoal, and Iron Ore. These rich colors add depth to your garage door and work beautifully with modern or traditional exteriors.</p><p>If you love the warmth of wood but want the durability of steel, the Ultra-Grain&reg; finishes in Medium, Cherry, or Walnut offer a realistic wood-look texture without the upkeep of a traditional wood door. If you need a specific color, the ColorBlast&reg; custom paint program lets you match nearly any color scheme, with more than 1,500 custom shades available.</p><p>Keep in mind that not all colors or finishes are available on every model, so be sure to check which options work for your chosen design.</p><p><em>*Available on select models.<br /><a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg;</a> Custom Paint Option Available.<br />**Promotion valid on new door purchases in the Iron Ore color; savings vary by door size and location.</em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"<p>With the Classic&trade; Steel collection, you can tailor the top of your garage door, whether you want extra light, a decorative accent, or an uninterrupted look. Choose from a variety of solid top sections for a simple appearance, or get creative with decorative insert windows like Colonial, Charleston, Stockton, Madison, Prairie, and several Sunset styles. The Architectural Series offers everything from plain glass to grilles in rectangles or squares, arches, and even elegant wrought iron-inspired designs. There are also special double door top sections and unique arch window options for wider openings.</p><p><em>*Acrylic window designs.<br />**Available only on 2\" thick 3-Layer doors only.<br />***Sunset Windows not available on Ultra-Grain&reg; doors.</em></p>","HardwareDisclaimer":"","DesignDisclaimer":"<p>Depending on door height, exact door appearance and number of sections may be different than illustrations above. <a href=\"http://clopaypdfs.com/pdf_files/RSDR-RESISTACKGUIDE-20.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" data-sf-ec-immutable=\"\">Click here</a> for complete details.</p>","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Modern Steel™","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/modern-steel-flush_fullview-window-black-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=db7014e9_14","Id":"170","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/modern-steel-collection","DisplayIndex":7,"ShortDescription":"Subtle modern beauty, simple up-keep","AlternativeText":"Modern Steel"},{"Title":"Gallery<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Steel","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/gallery-steel-ug-long-rec14-595.webp?sfvrsn=a7ceae04_9","Id":"12","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/gallerysteel","DisplayIndex":8,"ShortDescription":"Grooved panel steel carriage house garage doors","AlternativeText":"Gallery Steel"},{"Title":"Classic™ Wood","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/classic-wood-design-short-stockton-window-cedar-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=91462566_2","Id":"23","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/classicwood","DisplayIndex":20,"ShortDescription":"Enhance the natural character of your home with a handcrafted Classic™ Wood garage door","AlternativeText":"Classic Wood"}],"ProductBrochures":[{"Title":"Classic Premium Brochure","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-prem3layerss-13-copy.webp?sfvrsn=834e0748_3","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-PREM3LAYERSS-13.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Classic Steel Value Plus Brochure","ImageUrl":"https://www.